parameters: I was called... So, what is it that you need?
(Is she really curious about me... But, I...)
I'm sorry... I already have a partner.

I knew about the summoning magic. And I heard
about the magic circle from Hiyo.
What kind of information source do you have?

That... I heard various things from an
acquaintance...
Because I have a friend who is a magician.

......I investigated your and Amelia Blanchette's
backgrounds.

The reason I wasn't in the classroom was because
of the off-campus training.
The results are all nonsense, aren't they?

(How did she investigate... No, more importantly,
because of my unnecessary actions, things have
become troublesome.)

What is your purpose? Depending on your response,
I might restrain you here.

(I need Vice President Olivia's power... I want
her to become a comrade like Elena and Hiyo.)

(If that's the case, I have no choice but to
talk...)

The Kingdom's Magic Division is trying to stop the
summoning of demons...

Certainly, suspicious grimoires were found in the
Magic Research Club. It doesn't seem like
nonsense.
I see, I understand the situation.

But there's one more thing... What's the reason
behind your abnormally high magical power?
And, I also feel a very eerie magical power.

(Eerie... Could it be Leviathan's magical
power...?)

So Vice President Olivia can sense people's
magical power, huh?

Ordinary people can't do it. It's a talent you're
born with.

As for my magical power... I don't even understand
it myself.

I've studied various things on my own, so maybe
I'm a little different from other students.
(It seems like she reluctantly accepted it...)

Speaking of magic circles, even if it's not in the
Magic Research Club, there should be one somewhere
on campus.
We need to find it quickly.

Not much yet... so I want Vice President Olivia to
help me.

...As the Vice President, I must protect the
security of the academy.

If there is someone trying to summon a demon, we
must definitely stop them.

For now, I'll help... but I'll also be keeping an
eye on you.

Whether or not to restrain you will be decided
later.
May I ask about this academy right away?
I want to ask about the student council president.

Student Council President... Unfortunately, there
is no position for a Student Council President at
Caledonia Magic Academy.

But... there is information that suggests the
Student Council President is involved in summoning
demons.

Even so, the position of the student council
president has been vacant for decades.

(Even the Vice President didn't have any
information?)

However, the Student Council President's office
does exist in the records.

There is no president's office in this student
council room. But the term 'president's office'
appears in past records.
I don't know why, but it seems to be hidden.

(Is it relevant... but why did they hide the
president's office...)
Have you figured out where it is?

There is a closed door at the back of the student
council room.

It seems like previous student council members
didn't open it, but out of curiosity, I ended up
opening it.
There was a passage that continued.

Beyond that, there were many high-level monsters,
so we couldn't proceed.
Such a dangerous place within the academy...

According to the building's blueprint, there is
supposed to be nothing beyond that door.
I don't know who made it or when.

And even I, because it's dangerous, was stopped by
the faculty.

Even Vice President Olivia... if that's the case,
no one can go.

If it's just me, then... That's why I was looking
for someone to help me.
Hiyo alone... but that's not enough.
With your magical power, you might be able to go.
(Without realizing it... you've become so strong)

(Leviathan's magical power... no, it's not just
that)

If there's a chance that the student council
president has information, I'll go.

You're talking about something interesting, aren't
you?
Elena... and Hiyo and Amelia too

I'm sorry, I overheard your conversation outside
the room.

I accidentally overheard when I was guiding Amelia
to the student council room.

I didn't know there was such a secret in the
student council room.
I'm not going to play, you know.
I understand. But don't we need a healer?
Then Elena would be perfect, right?

I haven't told many people, but I'm good at
healing magic.

(Honestly, it's helpful. Maybe it's because of the
strange loop effect)
...If Hiyo says so, I don't mind.
Amelia... Were you okay during childbirth?
Yeah... It was over quickly, so I'm fine.

(I don't think she's okay... Being attacked by a
demon dog and giving birth are things she'll never
be able to forget for the rest of her life.)

(If it loops... No, that's no good. That would
play right into the enemy's hands.)

It seems like I've told the Vice President about
various things.

Ah, it seems like the Vice President already found
out that my background was a lie.
Aren't you too quick to believe in people?

Besides, I've been making various decisions on my
own...
But, there's no time to waste.
I'm sorry, I've been slowing you down.
No, that's not what I meant.

But I think it wouldn't be strange for a demon to
be summoned at any time.

There are more skilled magicians in this academy
than I thought.
Yeah, that's right. I was completely useless.
Well then, since it's getting dark, shall we go?
For now, let's go as far as we can today.
If it seems impossible, let's turn back.
The door is at the back here.

Olivia and the others have joined! You can change
the members in the menu.
